{"tid":904498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憂2047年變國安法 田北俊「轉軚」：為23條立法有著數","createTime":"2018-11-16T11:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T13:02:32.000Z","uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6456cdef98c7a50900aa107ccab5a981dc81903c","tid":904498,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:35:44.000Z","msg":"曾於2003年突然倒戈反對廿三條立法的自由黨榮譽主席田北俊，接受傳媒訪問時「轉軚」，認為應盡快為基本法廿三條立法，擔心愈遲立法條文將愈「辣」，到得2047年時，更甚可能演變成「國安法」。<br />\n<br />\n田北俊早上在一電台節目中表示，國家經濟越來越好，香港的議價能力正在下降，在形勢不如人的情況下應審時度勢，盡快為廿三條立法。他分析指，為廿三條立法其實對港「有著數」，因可制衡港府以不同的行政手段去處事，如DQ參選人資格等。<br />\n<br />\n至於一旦立法，田北俊估計會以2003年時擱置的草案作起點，並相信會是「加辣版」，辣度則視乎中央及港人可接受的程度。<br />\n<br />\n回顧2003年7月，時任自由黨主席的田北俊突然倒戈反對23條立法。當年，田北俊為求政府押後恢復二讀《國安法》草案（23條）而辭任行政會議成員，成為首位因與行會立場不同而請辭的行會成員，而此舉亦因而叫停了23條立法。<br />\n<br />\n當年的7月6日，田北俊在立法會就《國家安全條例草案》進行二讀辯論前，一向支持法案條文內容的他突然宣布不支持於7月9日進行二讀，並即時辭去行會職務。由於欠缺自由黨於立法會的支持，條例草案將無法通過，當時行政長官董建華於7月7日凌晨宣布撤回草案。董建華指，政府並無立法時間表，會在得到社會支持時才展開立法程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1365864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1365864%2F&d=sRrxY5Lmh0EsIZRmgEcxMUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=35ef2807\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1365864%2F&h=f43c60bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1365864/</a>"},{"pid":"6d1cad4f7856065d21de8efde4f0dede5278072f","tid":904498,"uid":15815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42dacfdd556018c8f6a1da460747183a32fe5ea","tid":904498,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"Come baby! 嚟啦，我不入地獄誰入地獄，大家一齊嚟攬炒<br />\n<br />\n為成功爭取2019年美國取消香港關係法鋪路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447c3d4b7954863680b6f2e8d66050123c191fc3","tid":904498,"uid":1372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全力支持23條立法，廢除香港關係法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ecb62f7d1d3821630d2c2c82985e67bfd9eea9","tid":904498,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"佢想建立攬炒黨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f73dd32b7fbba62a975a1ea4e35a4c702f4edba","tid":904498,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"白鳩痴，2047立國安法同而家23條立法有乜關係"},{"pid":"d4914a20164b2c21ff3bc42a49bd2353adf5a967","tid":904498,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"田大少識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}